<br>
I'm no tech master, but my guess: Faster connection will have no effect on your video performance. The things that are transfered over the phone line are like mob position, other player's positions, text from other players, and hps and mana pools. Your computer also estimates your mana pool and other pc/npc position in case it doesn't get the next info packet in time(this is why you sometimes see 'ghosts' and also creates phantom mana)<br>
<br>
